      "content": "It's like you're stuck in a never-ending nightmare, and the only way to wake up is to give in to the despair. But here's the thing: you can't just give up. You're not just fighting for a future, you're fighting for a moment, a single day, a single breath. Every decision you make, every action you take, is a tiny rebellion against the crushing weight of it all. So, don't give up, don't lose faith. You're not just trying to build a life, you're trying to build a spark of hope in a world that seems determined to snuff it out.",
